    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not just random vibration. i've been timing it. it's not a constant drone, it's like... three short pulses, then a long pause, then two short ones. it feels too deliberate to be just some transformer acting up. it's like there's an actual signal layered under the noise. does that even make sense? like, could frequencies actually be used to change how people feel?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
